## Dataset

This work uses the **Indian Diabetic Retinopathy Image Dataset (IDRiD)** for diabetic retinopathy grading experiments.

### Official Dataset Source

* IDRiD Dataset (IEEE DataPort): https://ieee-dataport.org/open-access/indian-diabetic-retinopathy-image-dataset-idrid

